RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.Module_Code, a.Contract_Ref_No, a.Counterparty, c.Short_Name, a.User_Ref_No FROM Oltbs_Contract a, Oltms_Customer c WHERE a.Module_Code IN ('LB', 'FC', 'OL') AND a.Branch = Global.Current_Branch AND a.Contract_Status IN ('A', 'Y', 'L') AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Olvw_Avl_Prod_Br_Usr b, Olvw_User_Products s WHERE s.User_Id = b.User_Id AND s.Product_Code = b.Product_Code AND a.Product_Code = b.Product_Code AND a.Branch = b.Branch_Code AND s.User_Id = Global.User_Id) AND c.Customer_No = a.Counterparty

SELECT DISTINCT b.Entity_Type FROM Oltms_Customer_Entity a, Oltms_Customer_Entity_Details b WHERE Nvl(a.Record_Stat, 'C') = 'O' AND Nvl(a.Auth_Stat, 'U') = 'A' AND a.Customer_No = b.Customer_No AND Nvl(?, 'EN') = 'ET' ORDER BY b.Entity_Type

SELECT * FROM (SELECT a.Customer_No, b.Short_Name FROM Lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers a, Oltms_Customer b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND a.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(Version_No) FROM Lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ?) AND a.Customer_No = b.Customer_No MINUS SELECT a.Counterparty, b.Customer_Name1 FROM Oltbs_Ffmt_Party a, Oltms_Customer b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND a.Ffmt_Ref_No = ? AND a.Counterparty = b.Customer_No) WHERE ? <> 'OL' UNION (SELECT * FROM (SELECT a.Customer_No, b.Short_Name FROM Lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers a, Oltms_Customer b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND a.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(Version_No) FROM Lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ?) AND a.Customer_No = b.Customer_No MINUS SELECT a.Counterparty, b.Customer_Name1 FROM Oltbs_Ffmt_Party a, Oltms_Customer b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND a.Counterparty = b.Customer_No) WHERE ? = 'OL')

SELECT * FROM ((SELECT DISTINCT a.Entity, b.Entity_Name, b.Entity_Type, a.Primary FROM Lbtbs_Borrower_Entities a, Oltms_Customer_Entity_Details b WHERE a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND a.Customer_No = ? AND a.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(Version_No) FROM Lbtbs_Borrower_Entities WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ?) AND a.Customer_No = b.Customer_No AND a.Entity = b.Entity AND ((b.Entity_Type = ? AND ? = 'ET') OR (? = 'EN')) AND ? <> 'OL') UNION (SELECT DISTINCT b.Entity, b.Entity_Name, b.Entity_Type, NULL AS Primary FROM Oltm_Customer_Entity a, Oltm_Customer_Entity_Details b WHERE a.Customer_No = b.Customer_No AND Nvl(a.Record_Stat, 'C') = 'O' AND Nvl(a.Auth_Stat, 'U') = 'A' AND a.Customer_No = ? AND ((b.Entity_Type = ? AND ? = 'ET') OR (? = 'EN')) AND ? = 'OL')) ORDER BY Entity
select media,description from mstms_media where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'

SELECT Message_Code, Template_Desc, Message ,b_Or_p FROM Oltms_Message_Template a WHERE Nvl(a.Record_Stat, 'C') = 'O' AND Nvl(a.Auth_Stat, 'U') = 'A' AND ((? IS NULL AND a.Message_Type = ? AND a.b_Or_p NOT IN (Decode(?, 'N', 'C', 'B'), 'B') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Cstm_Udf_Vals b WHERE b.Function_Id = 'OLDFFTMP' AND b.Field_Name = 'NAMEDAGENT' AND b.Rec_Key LIKE a.Message_Type || '~' || a.Message_Code || '~' AND b.Field_Val IS NOT NULL)) OR (? IS NOT NULL AND b_Or_p IN ('P', 'C') AND a.Message_Code IN (SELECT REPLACE(Substr(Rec_Key, (Instr(Rec_Key, '~', 1, 1)), (Instr(Rec_Key, '~', 1, 2))), '~', '') FROM Cstm_Udf_Vals u WHERE u.Function_Id = 'OLDFFTMP' AND u.Field_Name = 'NAMEDAGENT' AND u.Field_Val = ?)))
SELECT DISTINCT Event_Code, Event_Descr FROM Oltbs_Event ORDER BY Decode(Event_Code, 'DNOT', 1, 'EXFX', 2, 'IRFX', 3, 'NOTC', 4, 5)
SELECT Property_Code FROM Oltms_Property_Master WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ? AND Auth_Stat = 'A' AND Record_Stat = 'O'
SELECT DISTINCT (Component) FROM Oltbs_Amount_Due WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ? AND Component_Type = 'F' AND Basis_Amount_Tag = 'USERINPUT' AND Basis_Amount_Tag = 'USERINPUT'

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT Location FROM Oltms_Cust_Address_Ms WHERE Customer_No = ? AND Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A'

SELECT * FROM ((SELECT * FROM (SELECT Tag_Name, Substr(Tag_Name, 2, (Length(Tag_Name) - 2)) Tag_Desc FROM Oltbs_Fft_Advice_Tags WHERE Module = ? AND Event = ? AND ? IS NOT NULL /*Event*/ UNION (SELECT * FROM (SELECT Tag_Name, Substr(Tag_Name, 2, (Length(Tag_Name) - 2)) Tag_Desc FROM Oltb_Module_Fft_Tags WHERE Module = 'AL' UNION SELECT Tag_Name, Substr(Tag_Name, 2, (Length(Tag_Name) - 2)) Tag_Desc FROM Oltb_Module_Fft_Tags WHERE Module = ? AND /*Module Code */ Tag_Origin = 'S' UNION SELECT Tag_Name, Substr(Tag_Name, 2, (Length(Tag_Name) - 2)) Tag_Desc FROM Oltb_Module_Fft_Tags WHERE Module = ? AND /*Module Code */ Tag_Origin = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', (Decode(?, /*PRD*/ 'C', 'G', 'P')), 'LP', 'S', NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Parent*/ UNION SELECT Tag_Name, Substr(Tag_Name, 2, (Length(Tag_Name) - 2)) Tag_Desc FROM Oltb_Module_Fft_Tags WHERE Module = ? AND /*Module Code */ Tag_Origin = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', (Decode(?, /*PRD*/ 'C', NULL, 'G')), NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Gparent*/ UNION SELECT '_US$' || Field_Name || 'UE$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_Product_Userdef_Fields WHERE Product_Code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) UNION SELECT '_PUS$' || Field_Name || 'PUE$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_Product_Userdef_Fields WHERE Product_Code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) UNION SELECT '_UDF$' || Field_Name || 'UDF$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', (Decode(?, /*PRD*/ 'C', NULL, 'OLDTRONL')), NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Drfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT '_TUDF$' || Field_Name || 'TUDF$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', 'OLDTRONL', NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Trfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT '_FUDF$' || Field_Name || 'FUDF$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', 'FCTRONL', 'FC', 'FCDTRONL', NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Fcfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT '_UDFDESC$' || Field_Name || 'UDFDESC$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', (Decode(?, /*PRD*/ 'C', NULL, 'OLDTRONL')), NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Drfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT '_PUDFDESC$' || Field_Name || 'PUDFDESC$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LP', 'LPDCOMNT', NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Ptfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT '_FUDFDESC$' || Field_Name || 'FUDFDESC$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', 'FCTRONL', 'FC', 'FCDTRONL', NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Fcfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT '_TUDFDESC$' || Field_Name || 'TUDFDESC$_', Field_Name Tag_Desc FROM Oltm_User_Fields WHERE Function_Id = (Decode(?, /*MOD */ 'LB', 'OLDTRONL', NULL)) /*:Parameter.Prm_Trfun_Id*/ UNION SELECT b.Tag_Name, b.Tag_Desc FROM Oltms_Fft_Tags_Master a, Oltms_Fft_Tags_Detail b WHERE a.Message_Type = b.Message_Type AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND a.Message_Type = 'C') WHERE ? IS NULL /*Event*/)) WHERE ? = 'C') UNION (SELECT b.Tag_Name, b.Tag_Desc FROM Oltms_Fft_Tags_Master a, Oltms_Fft_Tags_Detail b WHERE a.Message_Type = b.Message_Type AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND a.Message_Type = 'P' AND ? = 'P'))
